# Linux Binary Releases
named aptly after godmode. all designed to target aqua bones player model.

`[god]` - _(SimpleCNN)_ The original designed for [ioQuake3](https://ioquake3.org/).
`[god2]` - _(SimpleCNN)_ QuakeLive & ioQuake3.
`[god3]` - _(SimpleCNN)_ QuakeLive & ioQuake3 with sampler for creating datasets.
`[fgod]` - _(FNN)_ QuakeLive & ioQuake3 with sampler for creating datasets. This is more generalised and will target all models but aqua bones best.
